      <p>Stefanie (Ph.D. University of Bremen) is a corpus linguist in the Department of Linguistics whose research focuses on variation in native and learner language, student writing, and second language acquisition. Prof. Wulff is co-editor of the <i>Cognitive Linguistics in Practice</i> book series published by John Benjamins.</p><br/>
