      <p>Ryan is an associate professor of Professional and Technical Communication and the deputy editor-in-chief of <i>IEEE Transactions on Professional Communication</i>. He received his PhD and MA in Technical Communication and Rhetoric from Texas Tech University and a graduate certificate in Teaching English to Speakers of Other Languages (TESOL) from Pennsylvania State University.</p><br/>
